commodities.tests
Class TestIdentifier

java.lang.Object
  commodities.tests.TestIdentifier
public class TestIdentifier
extends Object

The TestIdentifier class contains the Test Id and the class used for the test so that the TestManager can track which tests are best for a given commodity. This information comes from the test_xref table.
